%-----------SUMMARY-------------------
\section{Summary}
I am currently working as a Senior Data Scientist at Shopify. I have over fourteen
years of industry experience, solving data science problems using  machine learning, optimization
and statistics.
My research area during my master's degree was reinforcement learning; in particular,
function approximation for value iteration and Q learning.
Over the last three years at Shopify, I have also worked on
developing my data engineering skills, building ETL pipelines using PySpark and
DBT. 


